'''Happy's Landing''' was an ale house on [[Druckenwell/Legends|Druckenwell]]. Situated in [[Il Avali]]'s bad quarter, the establishment was dimly lit and quiet on afternoons, but provided music and spicy foods along with a drink selection including [[Elba water]] and [[TrooperBreath]].

[[Tinian I'att Azur-Jamin|Tinian I'att]] and [[Daye Azur-Jamin]] frequented this tavern during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

